{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review existing laws and rules to ensure asylum seekers can access transplants",
        "additional_details": "We call on the Government to review existing rules to ensure access is determined by clinical need rather than immigration status, guaranteeing fair, life-saving care for all.",
        "background": "We are concerned that the \u201cordinary residence\u201d rule and related NHS policies are preventing asylum seekers from being placed on transplant waiting lists, even in life-threatening cases. ",
